data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this 3-bed, 2-bath home on a generous .89-acre lot. Cozy up by the ventless fireplace in the inviting living space. The kitchen comes fully equipped with kitchen appliances, making meal prep a breeze. Enjoy the added convenience of an in-house washer and dryer. With spacious bedrooms and a large lot, this home offers a serene retreat with room to grow. Brand new roof and heat pump installed in 2023. Large storage building included in the backyard! Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
